data.description: 180 degree water views! This beautifully renovated home is perfect for entertaining. A storage unit has been added to the property and you'll find the downstairs to be perfect for parking or outdoor lounging. The upstairs has been tastefully designed with custom lighting and paint. Enjoy unobstructed water views from your kitchen living, dining and master or your gorgeous back deck. The open floorplan is the perfect setting for your dinner parties! New flooring, new interior paint, new custom lighting, full kitchen renovation, this property will take your breath away! This property comes with an additional parcel making the grounds over an acre. This peaceful cul-de-sac in a family friendly, Ocean Springs school district, neighborhood is a gem! Convenient to all Ocean Springs has to offer, you can be downtown in a matter of minutes and reach coffee shops and grocery stores, I10 or the Sports Complex in no time! Come see this beautiful, comfortable, coastal home today!
